Freshman Frida Gustafsson Spang posted a final round 3under par   moving up  spots and finishing second at the  UCF Challenge Tuesday afternoon PERIOD The threeday 54hole event was held at the RedTail Golf Club in Sorrento Fla PERIOD

Sitting in a tie for twelfth heading into the final  holes Gustafsson Spang  registered birdies on the seventh tenth and fourteenth holes and played even round golf on the other  to claim her third topsix placement of her rookie season PERIOD The Kinna Sweden native finished ahead of four Top50 players and ranked among the tournament leaders in par4 scoring 2nd3. birdies t5th10 and total pars t5th38 PERIOD
